  "description": "To double down in [blackjack](../index.md) is to double the original [wager](../../../terms/wager.md) in exchange for committing to receive exactly one additional card [@thorp1966]. The action increases both risk and reward: the player invests more precisely when the expected value of one more card is favorable enough to justify the larger stake.",
